id.description: The unique identifier of the satisfaction rating entry.

assignee_id.description: The unique identifier of the user assigned to the ticket.

group_id.description: The unique identifier of the group associated with the ticket.

reason_id.description: The unique identifier of the selected satisfaction rating reason.

requester_id.description: The unique identifier of the requester who provided the rating.

ticket_id.description: The unique identifier of the ticket associated with the satisfaction rating.

updated_at.description: The date and time when the satisfaction rating was last updated.

created_at.description: The date and time when the satisfaction rating was created.

url.description: The URL to access the details of the satisfaction rating.

score.description: The satisfaction score given by the requester (usually a numeric value).

reason.description: The reason selected by the requester for the satisfaction rating.

comment.description: The feedback comment provided by the requester.
